OL,3,CBereaved father hopes for answers as
OL,4,COmagh inquiry commences
OL,6,FHope has been expressed that the Omagh
OL,7,FBombing Inquiry will be the "beginning
OL,8,Fof the end" for the bereaved in their
OL,9,Fpursuit of answers.
OL,11,FMichael Gallagher, whose son Aiden was
OL,12,Fkilled in the 1998 dissident
OL,13,Frepublican bomb attack in the Co
OL,14,FTyrone town, also pressed the British
OL,15,Fand Irish governments to fully co-
OL,16,Foperate with the inquiry.
OL,18,FThe inquiry will examine whether the
OL,19,Fatrocity could have been prevented.
