OL,3,CBereaved father hopes for answers as
OL,4,COmagh inquiry commences
OL,6,FIt started four weeks of commemorative
OL,7,Fhearings on Tuesday, remembering the
OL,8,Fvictims and hearing from those who
OL,9,Fwere injured or directly affected.
OL,11,FMr Gallagher campaigned for many years
OL,12,Ffor an inquiry, and took the legal
OL,13,Faction which resulted in a judge in
OL,14,F2021 finding it was plausible there
OL,15,Fwas a real prospect the bombing could
OL,16,Fhave been prevented by the security
OL,17,Fservices, and calling for new
OL,18,Finvestigations on both sides of the
OL,19,FIrish border.
