OL,3,CBereaved father hopes for answers as
OL,4,COmagh inquiry commences
OL,6,FIn 2023, the UK government announced
OL,7,Fthere would be an independent
OL,8,Fstatutory inquiry into the bombing.
OL,10,FRuairi de Burca, director-general at
OL,11,Fthe Irish Department of Foreign
OL,12,FAffairs, attended the first public
OL,13,Fhearing of the Omagh inquiry last July.
OL,15,FHe told the inquiry that he was
OL,16,Fpresent on behalf of his government to
OL,17,Fsignal in the "clearest terms, our
OL,18,Fcommitment to facilitating and
OL,19,Fsupporting the work of this inquiry".
