OL,3,CBereaved father hopes for answers as
OL,4,COmagh inquiry commences
OL,6,FMr Gallagher said on Tuesday: "I just
OL,7,Fhope for me that this is the beginning
OL,8,Fof the end, that we do get the answers
OL,9,Fwe need, that both the British
OL,10,Fgovernment and the Irish government
OL,11,Ffully co-operate with the inquiry and
OL,12,Fas a bereaved parent I can say that's
OL,13,Fall I can do.
OL,15,F"I'm very grateful for everybody who
OL,16,Fhelped us get to this point where we
OL,17,Fcan see an end."
