OL,6,FMr Gallagher also praised the focus on
OL,7,Fthe victims in this phase of the
OL,8,Finquiry as "bringing humanity" to
OL,9,Fproceedings.
OL,11,F"It's important to be here to support
OL,12,Fthe other families, the Spanish
OL,13,Ffamilies are giving evidence this
OL,14,Fmorning, it's going to be difficult,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
